# Color

**Status: No color palette is approved.**

The mark is currently black-on-white only, and should remain black-on-white (or black on a light/neutral background) in all V1 uses.

A colorized version of this logo was explored and was explicitly rejected. Green/gold or any other brand color palette should not be introduced without explicit direction. Anyone extending this brand — including AI assistance — should treat the absence of color as the current deliberate state, not an oversight to be filled in.

---

# Usage Guidelines

- Use the icon-only mark for small or square placements (app icon, favicon).
- Use the horizontal lockup wherever the full wordmark and tagline fit.
- Use the transparent-background export when placing the logo over a colored or textured surface (e.g. packaging photography, delivery truck livery).
- Use the white-background export where a transparent file isn't supported or a clean rectangle is preferred.
- Do not stretch, recolor, rotate, or alter the proportions of the mark.
- Do not use a stacked lockup — none is currently approved.

